{
  "id": "69a54425f23b102a0530895b",
  "title": "公開するべき議論、しない議論とは何か",
  "created": 1772438572,
  "updated": 1772439959,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a54425f23b102a0530895b",
      "text": "公開するべき議論、しない議論とは何か",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438572,
      "updated": 1772438572
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5443500000000001172c8",
      "text": "例を列挙してみよう #書いてけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438581,
      "updated": 1772438604
    },
    {
      "id": "69a545c100000000001172d8",
      "text": "\t謎の記号（[$ \\square\\Diamond]）については（[様相論理]、[義務論理]を参照）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438977,
      "updated": 1772439030
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5473c00000000001172e2",
      "text": "\tべき論は客観的な事実としての書き込みができないのでスタンプが必須になる[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439356,
      "updated": 1772439404
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5475c00000000001172e3",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439388,
      "updated": 1772439867
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5442c00000000001172c5",
      "text": "公開するべき議論[$ (\\square P)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438572,
      "updated": 1772438808
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5449600000000001172d0",
      "text": " 税金の項目を決定するための議論[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438678,
      "updated": 1772439342
    },
    {
      "id": "69a546d800000000001172e0",
      "text": " 社会保障の項目を決定するための議論[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439256,
      "updated": 1772439345
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5443d00000000001172ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438589,
      "updated": 1772439727
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5484000000000001172e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439616,
      "updated": 1772439616
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5446200000000001172cd",
      "text": "公開しないべき（してはならない）議論[$ \\square(\\lnot P)=\\lnot\\Diamond P]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438626,
      "updated": 1772438882
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5465500000000001172dc",
      "text": " 患者の余命を宣告するかしないか、病名を告げるか告げないかの議論は患者自身に公開されてはならない[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439125,
      "updated": 1772439336
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5465800000000001172dd",
      "text": " \t話が拗れるだけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439128,
      "updated": 1772439217
    },
    {
      "id": "69a546e5000000000030579d",
      "text": "\t社員Aを解雇するかどうかの議論（A本人に公開してはならぬ）もここかな？[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1772439270,
      "updated": 1772439294
    },
    {
      "id": "69a545a200000000001172d6",
      "text": " 国防に関する詳細な議論[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438946,
      "updated": 1772439324
    },
    {
      "id": "69a547bf00000000001172e4",
      "text": "\t他国を攻撃するための計画に関する詳細な議論[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439487,
      "updated": 1772439581
    },
    {
      "id": "69a546e800000000001172e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439272,
      "updated": 1772439272
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5447d00000000001172cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438653,
      "updated": 1772439713
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172ec",
      "text": "公開するべきではない議論[$ \\lnot(\\square P)]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172ed",
      "text": "\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172f0",
      "text": "公開しないべきではない（してもよい）議論[$ \\lnot\\square(\\lnot P)=\\Diamond P]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172f1",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548b400000000001172f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439732,
      "updated": 1772439732
    },
    {
      "id": "69a548ba00000000001172f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439738,
      "updated": 1772439738
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5443d00000000001172cb",
      "text": "[bg.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438589,
      "updated": 1772439627
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5445000000000001172cc",
      "text": "[*** 文章での議論ゾーン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772438608,
      "updated": 1772439896
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5497700000000001172f4",
      "text": "\t上の分類に意義がある時に議論が始まる[異議あり！.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772439927,
      "updated": 1772439959
    },
